<doc id="443272" wikidata="Q521441" url="?curid=443272" title="Anneux">
<text>Anneux () is a commune in the Nord department in northern France.

Its church is dedicated to Saint Léger.

==History==
Anneux was among the villages fought over at the western end of the Battle of Cambrai (1917).

==Population==
===Heraldry===
==See also==
